name: CaliforniaCourtroomNews
0:
”Alexa, what's my Flash Briefing?”
”Alexa, play my Flash Briefing”
skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
des:
Upon asking a Courtroom News, Alexa will let the user know one of the California Courtroom News Headline.

Alexa Is using Flash Briefing API and pulling Headlines from "http://newsroom.courts.ca.gov/rss.xml"
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
